{"type":"message","id":"c925c25e","parentId":"7b69e654","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:21:30.821Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Perfect! I can see a long list of AI founders and startup founders on this page. I can see I'm already following Alexandr Wang. Now I need to systematically follow more AI founders. I can see many people with \"Follow\" buttons:\n\n1. Bruno Faviero (@Bfaviero) - 2x AI Defense founder - ref e3472\n2. Maxi Kuan (@dearseki) - AI Project founder - ref e3525\n3. Katie Mishra (@katieruthmishra) - VC-backed founder - ref e3568\n4. Khurram Zuberi (@kmzuberi) - AI, ML Founder - ref e3616\n5. Nimay Parekh (@nimayx) - Cyber + AI Founder - ref e3658\n6. Deepak Deolalikar (@ddeolalikar) - Co Founder Ziply AI - ref e3727\n7. Cameron Dennis (@Cameron_Dennis_) - Director of AI, Founder - ref e3769\n8. The Generative Beings (@tgbeings) - AI network - ref e3817\n9. luffy (@0xluffy) - founding @capydotai - ref e3872\n10. Nazar (@hre4anyk) - Building @regataai - ref e3917\n11. jeff lemo (@jeffreylemoine) - AI Founder - ref e3965\n12. Carlo Tortora Brayda (@tortorabrayda) - AI & Cybersecurity - ref e4007\n13. Sean O'Bannon (@seanob) - finance @Cranston_AI, founder - ref e4049\n14. Mellissah Smith (@marketingeyeaus) - AI marketing founder - ref e4095\n15. Plácido Doménech Espí (@PlacidoDomenech) - AI founder - ref e4141\n16. cyberh49.eth (@cyberh49) - AI researcher, Founder - ref e4203\n\n\n17. Raph. H. (@Rapahelz) - AI Founder - ref e4258\n18. Adam Cecchetti (@adamcecc) - Co-Founder/CEO Staris AI - ref e4300\n19. Zephyr Liu (@iurp) - AI Founder - ref e4342\n20. Claire (@claire_xiee) - 2x AI Founder - ref e4387\n21. Perks (@AiTechPerks) - AI influencer, Founder - ref e4432\n22. Suman Kanuganti (@SumanPersonalAI) - Founder @PersonalAI_ - ref e4483\n\nI've expanded the list with additional AI founders across various domains. The collection includes entrepreneurs in research, marketing, cybersecurity, and personal AI technologies. Each represents a unique perspective in the AI startup ecosystem. I'll continue the list of AI-related accounts, focusing on founders and innovative projects. These accounts represent diverse AI ventures, from stock prediction to job application technologies, highlighting the breadth of AI innovation across different domains.\n\nThe list includes additional AI founders and specialized platforms like LLM stock prediction, research-focused AI, and AI-driven job application tools. Each account represents a unique approach to leveraging artificial intelligence in different sectors. I'm strategizing an efficient approach to automate following AI founders. Batch clicking seems promising, but requires careful handling to manage rate limits. I'll start by testing a small group of follow buttons, closely monitoring X's API response. The goal is to systematically build a network while respecting platform constraints, balancing speed with responsible automation.\n\nMy initial test will focus on a controlled batch of 5-10 founder profiles, allowing me to assess the system's tolerance and potential limitations. This methodical approach ensures I don't trigger any rate restricting mechanisms.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I can see many AI founders on this page. Let me start following them systematically. I'll follow multiple accounts and track my progress."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4b839730f84e4e4e841d9306","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","profile":"openclaw","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e3472"},"targetId":"9018AFFA28ACF1BD8DA950B14B799552"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":16363,"output":908,"cacheRead":34624,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":51895,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772842864770}}
