{"type":"message","id":"8eb46fa7","parentId":"5bd5cd96","timestamp":"2026-03-07T00:25:36.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The browser is timing out again. Given the persistent technical difficulties with the browser service, let me provide a summary report based on what I was able to accomplish:\n\n1. Follows completed: Approximately 20 AI founders/startup founders (including Alexandr Wang, Bruno Faviero, Maxi Kuan, Katie Mishra, Khurram Zuberi, Nimay Parekh, Deepak Deolalikar, Cameron Dennis, The Generative Beings, luffy, Nazar, jeff lemo, Carlo Tortora Brayda, Sean O'Bannon, Mellissah Smith, Plácido Doménech Espí, cyberh49.eth, Raph. H., Adam Cecchetti, and Indie Hackers)\n\n2. Likes attempted: Tried to like multiple AI-related posts but encountered browser service timeouts\n\n3. Tweet to post: Still need to post 1 original tweet about AI in hospitality\n\nGiven the technical issues, let me try one more approach - let me navigate to the compose tweet page and post my tweet about AI in hospitality.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Due to browser service issues, let me focus on posting the tweet about AI in hospitality. Let me click the Post button:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6f947641388040dda619d48d","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"act","profile":"openclaw","request":{"kind":"click","ref":"e105"},"targetId":"9018AFFA28ACF1BD8DA950B14B799552"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zhipu","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1089,"output":307,"cacheRead":112896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114292,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772843122310}}
